    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tofu cubes are crisp and golden, reduce the heat to very low</p><p>Wait for the pan to cool down a little, then add the <strong>Marmite teriyaki sauce</strong></p><p>Cook for 1-2 min, stirring occasionally, until a thick, glossy sauce coats the tofu cubes</p>",
